• DDoS attack is more lethal than the DoS attack. The prevention of DDoS attacks
is very difficult as compared to the normal DoS attacks.
• The main difference is that the DoS attack is targeted from a specific origin of
traffic, while in the DDoS attack case, multiple sources of traffic are used to
attack the victim server (at the same time).
Impact
